{
  "stem": "9730.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I-- I-- I had a lot of so-called friends in those days, with whom we would play endlessly.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, living in the country, there were actually areas open to us that-- that someone growing up in a city would-- would never have.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had these woods.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We would take long hikes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We would explore the woods and-- and the mountains, and do hiking and swimming.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I also liked the movies a great deal.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- and every week, at least once, I-- I-- I would go to the weekend movie that was being shown in those days.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And, in that sense, I also learned a great deal about America that way.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] I'm trying.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For instance, I-- I know-- one of the things that I was absolutely wild about, and so were my friends in school, were westerns.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and there was, of course, Tom Mix was a big star in-- in-- in those days, with his-- I think his white horse by name of Trigger, if I'm not mistaken.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and we couldn't get enough of that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we played that out to the ultimate.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this was also reinforced by a series of-- of western stories written by a German author by name of Karl May, who wrote some very definitive works on-- on the American West and on the Indians and the plight of the Indians.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, somehow, through that, I always thought that somehow or other I would wind up in-- in America, and presumably in the west, where I now live.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I-- in that sense, it's-- it's quite funny that I should wind up here in Arizona.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "More than Jewish, simply because there weren't any.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I-- but I have to qualify that.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
